Pattern
- single tone;
- module;
- fabric;
- decorator;
******************************************************
Events
- add as attribute (<div onclick='alert('click')'>)
- foo.onclick = () => alert('click')
- foo.addEventListener('click', () => alert('click'))
- foo.removeEventListener('click', () => alert('click'))